{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-programs-js","path":"/programs/pagerduty-integration.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>The PagerDuty integration enables incidents to be created each time a new (high or critical severity) report is submitted or triaged onto HackerOne. This integration is flexible and can be used to create a PagerDuty incident for any of the <a href=\"https://api.hackerone.com/webhooks/#events\">events</a> listed.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> The PagerDuty integration is only available for Enterprise programs.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"set-up\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#set-up\" aria-label=\"set up permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Set up</h3>\n<p>To set up the integration between PagerDuty and each time a high or critical report is created on HackerOne:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Navigate to <strong>Configuration > Services</strong> on PagerDuty.</li>\n<li>Click on <strong>New Service</strong> or add an integration to an existing service on PagerDuty by clicking <strong>+Add New Services</strong> on your services page.</li>\n<li>Select <strong>HackerOne</strong> for the <em>Integration Type</em>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pagerduty set up\"\n        title=\"pagerduty set up\"\n        src=\"/static/dd18c2892a1e53395514f4aaf4de3582/0b533/pagerduty-step-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dd18c2892a1e53395514f4aaf4de3582/fac75/pagerduty-step-3.png 125w,\n/static/dd18c2892a1e53395514f4aaf4de3582/63868/pagerduty-step-3.png 250w,\n/static/dd18c2892a1e53395514f4aaf4de3582/0b533/pagerduty-step-3.png 500w,\n/static/dd18c2892a1e53395514f4aaf4de3582/1d69c/pagerduty-step-3.png 750w,\n/static/dd18c2892a1e53395514f4aaf4de3582/00d43/pagerduty-step-3.png 1000w,\n/static/dd18c2892a1e53395514f4aaf4de3582/57f7d/pagerduty-step-3.png 2088w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Click <strong>Add Service</strong>.</li>\n<li>Go to the <strong>Integrations</strong> tab on the <strong>Services</strong> page.</li>\n<li>Click on <strong>HackerOne</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pagerduty selecting the settings gear\"\n        title=\"pagerduty selecting the settings gear\"\n        src=\"/static/4036015e231eb752442f1705165c8615/0b533/pagerduty-step-6-new.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4036015e231eb752442f1705165c8615/fac75/pagerduty-step-6-new.png 125w,\n/static/4036015e231eb752442f1705165c8615/63868/pagerduty-step-6-new.png 250w,\n/static/4036015e231eb752442f1705165c8615/0b533/pagerduty-step-6-new.png 500w,\n/static/4036015e231eb752442f1705165c8615/1d69c/pagerduty-step-6-new.png 750w,\n/static/4036015e231eb752442f1705165c8615/00d43/pagerduty-step-6-new.png 1000w,\n/static/4036015e231eb752442f1705165c8615/e1250/pagerduty-step-6-new.png 1786w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>Copy the <strong>Integration URL</strong> and store that for later.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pagerduty integration url field\"\n        title=\"pagerduty integration url field\"\n        src=\"/static/401dffd6ccc8b155389911b82ee9c52e/0b533/pagerduty-step-7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/401dffd6ccc8b155389911b82ee9c52e/fac75/pagerduty-step-7.png 125w,\n/static/401dffd6ccc8b155389911b82ee9c52e/63868/pagerduty-step-7.png 250w,\n/static/401dffd6ccc8b155389911b82ee9c52e/0b533/pagerduty-step-7.png 500w,\n/static/401dffd6ccc8b155389911b82ee9c52e/1d69c/pagerduty-step-7.png 750w,\n/static/401dffd6ccc8b155389911b82ee9c52e/00d43/pagerduty-step-7.png 1000w,\n/static/401dffd6ccc8b155389911b82ee9c52e/e4d4a/pagerduty-step-7.png 2198w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"8\">\n<li>Log in to your account on hackerone.com.</li>\n<li>Navigate to your webhooks settings on <strong>Program Settings > Program > Webhooks</strong>.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>New Webhook</strong>.</li>\n<li>Paste the URL that was copied from the Pagerduty integration page in step 7.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"webhooks page\"\n        title=\"webhooks page\"\n        src=\"/static/5501538405c7001c83db2e7f6de287cf/0b533/pagerduty-step-11.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5501538405c7001c83db2e7f6de287cf/fac75/pagerduty-step-11.png 125w,\n/static/5501538405c7001c83db2e7f6de287cf/63868/pagerduty-step-11.png 250w,\n/static/5501538405c7001c83db2e7f6de287cf/0b533/pagerduty-step-11.png 500w,\n/static/5501538405c7001c83db2e7f6de287cf/1d69c/pagerduty-step-11.png 750w,\n/static/5501538405c7001c83db2e7f6de287cf/00d43/pagerduty-step-11.png 1000w,\n/static/5501538405c7001c83db2e7f6de287cf/062c8/pagerduty-step-11.png 1386w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"12\">\n<li>Select <strong>Report created</strong> and <strong>Report triaged</strong> as the events you want to trigger the webhook on.</li>\n<li><em>(Optional)</em> Select any other events you want to trigger the webhook on.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Add webhook</strong> to save the webhook.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Each new and triaged report that has a high or critical severity will now create an incident on PagerDuty and page the appropriate teams based on your PagerDuty policies. You can tailor the configuration of your integration for different use cases by adjusting the events in step 13.</p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/programs/pagerduty-integration.html","id":"programs/pagerduty-integration","title":"PagerDuty Integration","description":null},"headings":[{"value":"Set up"}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}